{"tid":2137171,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"頭痛問題","createTime":"2020-08-02T16:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T12:11:53.000Z","uid":199768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"df8cebc6be4fc59e9665c9c0ae0187556eedf9da","tid":2137171,"uid":199768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3746a3565c74eecbc3152f0a97e1aff397b4d5","tid":2137171,"uid":266621,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T17:16:03.000Z","msg":"可能係偏頭痛<br />\n食必理痛啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好訓太多同睇閃光"},{"pid":"7097faad4f7f270ff7e7fc6f91b9f22f007023b4","tid":2137171,"uid":233232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T17:20:57.000Z","msg":"同你位置差唔多 不過唔係痛 有啲緊咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ffc6faf56231d4943d495aa7983bcba81d0d3b2","tid":2137171,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T17:27:23.000Z","msg":"絲打？ 偏頭多"},{"pid":"fd435929521c8abec7455a2e8bc21379eb3fcdb7","tid":2137171,"uid":226669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T17:50:15.000Z","msg":"係咪吸收唔夠鐵質？"},{"pid":"859ca43c74ff9ab8d5fc7580d70dc951690b8b51","tid":2137171,"uid":2285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T17:56:12.000Z","msg":"一樣 係唔知點解呢排係咁"},{"pid":"5786dfba3c98fc299ce17b318e8346237e82a119","tid":2137171,"uid":199768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T19:23:21.000Z","msg":"回覆番上面咁多位巴絲，我自己覺得自己唔似偏頭痛，因為睇番偏頭痛似係會劇痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望過多排會好番，呢個時候有咩大病會好麻煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c856b8d99736801c08d1647046b082123789887d","tid":2137171,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T01:20:27.000Z","msg":"有冇可能有食物敏感，如麩質、蛋果類？"},{"pid":"bbac41ccff62557e911fc9dce41a7aa4950006f7","tid":2137171,"uid":104440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T01:33:49.000Z","msg":"可能用得電話多 低頭族"},{"pid":"5ac0569ab30cf410121f4903351434d1f100337f","tid":2137171,"uid":234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:20:09.000Z","msg":"我都係一樣，突然間左後方會抽痛<br />\n夜晚特別易發生你地係咪咁？"},{"pid":"97b997ed12ab9ddb5dfd03a3aef06b2e51a14aba","tid":2137171,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:18:19.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2Fx6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=5fbc471d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。<br />\n每射一次就傷身一次，包括做愛，夢遺（含精量唔多），而節制打Ｊ只不過係延遲你出症狀既時間／嚴重程度。<br />\n<br />\n每人體質唔同，症狀都唔同，以下為最常見：<br />\n早洩，變樣哀，猥瑣，臉色灰暗，自卑冇自信、腰痛<br />\n腦力下降，暗瘡，有口氣，脫髮、耳嗚、任何神經症<br />\n體臭，易怒，夜尿，表達能力差，社交恐懼症，雙眼無神，前列線炎<br />\n<br />\n戒丁必睇資料：<br />\n<br />\n戒為良藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2Fx6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=d05f8447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戒Ｊ需知： <br />\n<br />\n戒Ｊ後３個月內症狀加重／加深屬正常，係戒斷反應<br />\n<br />\n身體恢復過程並唔係直線上升，而係好似過山車咁上下移動，會不斷由壞轉好，好轉壞，但隨著時間既增長，身體會慢慢恢復，症狀慢慢消失<br />\n<br />\n夢遺唔當破戒，意淫都傷身，睇ＡＶ唔Ｊ一樣咁傷身 ，中醫：心動則精自走<br />\n<br />\n做愛都傷身，所以我地戒Ｊ恢復身體，身體好虧既戒返２年，之後再節制性行為，咁就唔會出症狀，飛翔老師推薦一月2次，就是腎氣充足的情況下，這樣對身體傷害較小。<br />\n<br />\n戒色唔係做和尚，係先禁慾養返好個身體，再同老婆／女友節制性生活，咁就唔會出症狀<br />\n<br />\n叫雞係比打丁更加嚴重既邪淫，如果你忍唔到，寧願你打丁，都唔好叫雞<br />\n<br />\n戒丁期間扑野唔算破戒，但你本身既症狀，唔洗諗住會恢復<br />\n<br />\n戒丁最好既方法就係睇戒色文章，想成功戒Ｊ就將（戒為良藥）睇一次<br />\n學習提升覺悟，覺悟降伏心魔，唔睇（戒為良藥），基本上只係等破戒"},{"pid":"6d89c4165f1bb936e078e3670fae1edac0823944","tid":2137171,"uid":51566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:21:08.000Z","msg":"我都係一個月前開始係咁頭痛<br />\n照過哂都無野 醫生講都係偏頭痛"},{"pid":"6618452296fb6913e0ebe6e947c9349c03dcb372","tid":2137171,"uid":84381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:22:09.000Z","msg":"我都係 成日頭痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73efa91980f76d8b77ec252fcbd65a80189e2fe2","tid":2137171,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:24:01.000Z","msg":"可能係頸影響到"},{"pid":"e306f6249b665a60131c290addecdacf8fc87e5a","tid":2137171,"uid":297465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df8cebc6be4fc59e9665c9c0ae0187556eedf9da","tid":2137171,"uid":199768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:11:53.000Z","msg":"應該唔夠vit B complex and D"}]}